t_rendered": "<p>不得不说 60hz 真的还好，刚手机切换过来可能会有点不适，但是用个 1 分钟就没什么感觉了。</p>\n<p>最难受的其实是 Touch ID ，Face ID 实在是太舒服和无感了。</p>\n<p>而且 mini 7 的 Touch ID 不是触摸解锁，锁屏的时候不仅得按下去，还得还得停留一会才能解锁，挺麻烦的。</p>\n<p>第二点就是太宽了，打字有些难受，本人手不算大，如果这个黑边能缩一半应该会好很多。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1738132380, "replies": 18, "id": 1108265}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 65641, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9212, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 582364, "username": "SeleiXi", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/SeleiXi", "website": "www.seleixi.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "SeleiXi", "btc": "", "location": "香港", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b45c/e619/582364_mini.png?m=1738154853", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b45c/e619/582364_normal.png?m=1738154853", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b45c/e619/582364_large.png?m=1738154853", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b45c/e619/582364_xlarge.png?m=1738154853", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b45c/e619/582364_xlarge.png?m=1738154853", "created": 1653185546, "last_modified": 1738154853}, "last_reply_by": "dvbs2000", "last_touched": 1738177118, "title": "28 届想找大厂暑假实习…这个简历有可改善的地方吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1108288", "created": 1738156220, "deleted": 0, "content": "![CV]( https://i.imgur.com/2w7CLt5.jpeg) \r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n但貌似申请暑假实习岗的时间已经过了…如果是内推的话还有机会吗？最近接了个外包，内容都可以自己包装而且最后也会上线，有必要多加个这样的项目来多套点八股文吗？可以用 java 来写，然后用同一份简历同时投 java 和 go 岗吗？感谢 v 友们！！", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"CV\" clas